<div type="edition" xml:lang="tel-Latn" rendition="class:telugu maturity:vernacular">

<p>
<lb n="1"/>Anupamamagu baṁḍāramu nanaghaṁbagu sandhivigrahi <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> bekkuni <unclear>yōga</unclear>ṁbuluṁ dējamugonakoni paḍasinayamātya kommaṁḍu vritini <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g>
<lb n="2"/>karagajakēṁdusaṁkhyaśakakālamuvolpuga bhāvapaṭṭu<unclear>dēvarani</unclear> nakhaṁḍadīpamati bāsuralīla veluṁgga nilpe vistaramatiṁ dallidaṁḍrulaku dharmmuvugā śaśi
<lb n="3" break="no"/>tārakaṁbugā gurubhujuṁ ḍiddhavikramuṁḍuṁ gommanaperggaḍa dhanyaṁ ḍunnati<unclear>ni</unclear> <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> svasti śrī śakavaruṣa<supplied reason="omitted">ṁbu</supplied>lu 1082 gunēṁṭi yuttarāyaṇanimittamuna svasti samastaprasasti
<lb n="4" break="no"/>sahita śrīmanmahāmaṁḍalēśvara kulōttuṁggacōḍagoṁkarājula śrīma<unclear>tsa</unclear>ṁndhivigrahi kommanapeggaḍa gammanāṁṭilōni bāvanārāyaṇadēvaraku nakhaṁḍadīpa
<lb n="5" break="no"/>mu <unclear>da</unclear>ma taṁḍri sandhivigrahi gōviṁdanapeggaḍakuṁ dama talli gētāsāniki dharmmārtthamugā nilpi brarmmanabōyini koḍku nāmanabōyinivasamuna nācaṁdrā
<lb n="6" break="no"/>rkkasthāyigā niccina mēṁkalu goṟiyaluṁgā 55 vīni<unclear>ṁ</unclear> jē koni nāmanabōyu<unclear>ṁḍu</unclear> putrāmapautrikamu nityamāneṁḍu neyi dīpamunaku naḍapaṁgalavāṁḍu <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g>
</p>

